1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:34,857
=Episode 21=
(I, Ye Zhao, want to be with Xi forever!)

3
00:00:35,980 --> 00:00:36,700
You good?

4
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:41,500
I saw you die in my arms.

5
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:47,740
That wouldn't be such a bad way to go.

6
00:00:48,957 --> 00:00:50,036
Look at the timing,

7
00:00:50,037 --> 00:00:51,597
and you're still joking.

8
00:00:57,125 --> 00:00:58,605
If I can die in your arms,

9
00:00:59,725 --> 00:01:01,165
I'd do it willingly.

10
00:01:01,462 --> 00:01:04,422
Since childhood,
I can see who is about to die.

11
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:06,900
That fate has

12
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:09,740
never changed.

13
00:01:10,060 --> 00:01:11,380
Don't forget.

14
00:01:12,212 --> 00:01:13,412
I'm a god.

15
00:01:13,925 --> 00:01:15,285
I'm not like everyone else.

16
00:01:18,460 --> 00:01:20,100
How's the root-seeking worm
coming along?

17
00:01:20,140 --> 00:01:22,420
If we destroy the demon root

18
00:01:22,460 --> 00:01:23,740
and remove the demon heart,

19
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:25,979
maybe everything can be resolved.

20
00:01:25,980 --> 00:01:27,460
It still needs time.

21
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:29,420
I'll finish refining it
as soon as possible.

22
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:33,180
Don't worry, I've got this.

23
00:01:36,175 --> 00:01:37,455
Xiao.

24
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:42,140
Baobao...

25
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:44,660
So that means...

26
00:01:48,475 --> 00:01:49,899
(Martial Hall)

27
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:51,500
Xiao, stop right there!

28
00:01:53,620 --> 00:01:54,660
Your Highness.

29
00:02:02,620 --> 00:02:03,780
My lady.

30
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:32,780
You're my mother,

31
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:37,940
and you're my father.

32
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,180
This is wonderful!

33
00:02:45,350 --> 00:02:47,699
I finally have a father and a mother!

34
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,540
I'm so happy!

35
00:02:50,325 --> 00:02:51,925
I'm happy too.

36
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:10,940
My blood...

37
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:17,380
D*mn heavens!

38
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:21,459
You've humiliated and toyed with me,

39
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:23,100
and I've endured it all!

40
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,780
I just want to be human again!

41
00:03:26,412 --> 00:03:28,459
I want my people to be human again!

42
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:30,060
What did I do wrong?

43
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:31,700
You are wrong.

44
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:33,459
Have you forgotten so quickly?

45
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:34,700
I didn't do anything wrong!

46
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:36,460
I've only done good!

47
00:03:37,020 --> 00:03:38,180
Back then,

48
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:40,740
I led the way
in consuming Ye Zhao's flesh

49
00:03:41,700 --> 00:03:43,540
to cure the Verdant Decay!

50
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:46,340
Wasn't that wrong?

51
00:03:47,820 --> 00:03:49,419
You turned all the sick

52
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,900
into Flower Slaves.

53
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:53,420
If they don't

54
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:55,699
drink human blood every day,

55
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:58,140
they suffer unbearable pain.

56
00:03:59,220 --> 00:04:00,420
Isn't all

57
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,780
of this your fault?

58
00:04:08,860 --> 00:04:10,540
I just want to live.

59
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:15,620
What's wrong with that?

60
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:19,460
I want Xi back.

61
00:04:20,140 --> 00:04:21,980
What did I do wrong?

62
00:04:22,420 --> 00:04:23,819
She's not Xi.

63
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:24,980
She's not!

64
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:26,979
She's not!

65
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:27,979
She's not!

66
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:30,419
She's not!

67
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:32,219
She's not!

68
00:04:32,220 --> 00:04:33,620
Yes! No!

69
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:34,540
Yes!

70
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:40,420
Tell me, what am I supposed to do?

71
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:44,019
You were the one
who told me Chu Xihe could save us!

72
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:46,300
You told me how to deal with Ye Zhao!

73
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:47,979
You said

74
00:04:47,980 --> 00:04:49,700
if I saved everyone,

75
00:04:49,740 --> 00:04:51,219
Xi would return!

76
00:04:51,220 --> 00:04:52,980
And now?

77
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:56,180
My people have all been captured.

78
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:58,900
I'm the only one left.

79
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:03,220
You still have me.

80
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:30,460
Wasn't Pei Xiao
supposed to have you locked up?

81
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:32,220
A mere prison is nothing.

82
00:05:32,660 --> 00:05:34,460
Switching with a substitute

83
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:36,780
is easy for me.

84
00:05:41,660 --> 00:05:42,660
Immortal,

85
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:45,259
if you had told me sooner
that Ye Zhao's flesh

86
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:46,780
could cure the Verdant Decay

87
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:49,580
and grant immortality as a Flower Slave,

88
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:50,900
I would have

89
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:52,740
taken a bite back then.

90
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:54,220
Now that the Emperor

91
00:05:54,625 --> 00:05:56,540
has stripped me of my military power,

92
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,900
what should we do?

93
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:04,532
Rescue my people.

94
00:06:07,020 --> 00:06:08,886
I have my ways.

95
00:06:08,887 --> 00:06:10,100
Of course.

96
00:06:10,437 --> 00:06:12,917
My shadow guards have all
contracted the Verdant Decay.

97
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:15,100
If we obtain Ye Zhao's flesh,

98
00:06:15,860 --> 00:06:18,900
they'll become unstoppable.

99
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:22,220
A golden core swallowed into the body,

100
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:25,540
and one realizes fate is one's own

101
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:27,540
to command!

102
00:06:28,260 --> 00:06:30,980
Father, watch closely from the heavens!

103
00:06:31,580 --> 00:06:32,460
From now on,

104
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,540
this world belongs to our family!

105
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:40,682
(Martial Hall)

106
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:46,420
(Zhao, focus on refining
the root-seeking worm inside.)

107
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:47,780
(I'll wait for you.)

108
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:05,780
Xi.

109
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:07,220
Today,

110
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,900
I sincerely ask again,

111
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:10,980
please marry me.

112
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:13,100
I have long admired you.

113
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:15,660
I'd like to stay beside you
as your partner.

114
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,659
Drop the act.

115
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:25,460
I haven't settled

116
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:27,420
all that blood on your hands.

117
00:07:28,340 --> 00:07:29,460
Xi,

118
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:32,340
do you feel any better now?

119
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:36,019
I'm not the one you think I am.

120
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:38,259
And you're not
that village chief anymore.

121
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:40,220
I'm Chu Xihe.

122
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:05,340
How could I think that?

123
00:08:06,580 --> 00:08:08,580
There's no way you're her.

124
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:18,180
Chu Xihe,

125
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:20,100
I'm here to help you.

126
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:23,420
I know how to completely
remove your demon heart.

127
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:25,459
Your Highness, something seems off.

128
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:26,740
Anything unusual?

129
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:31,860
Your Highness.

130
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:35,099
It's nothing. Stand down.

131
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,100
Yes.

132
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:40,180
If there's even a hint of a lie,

133
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,900
I'll lock you up until you die.

134
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:45,460
That ritual can

135
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:48,100
completely remove the demon root.

136
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:50,220
You will die,

137
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:52,420
but after reincarnation,

138
00:08:52,575 --> 00:08:54,535
you can still

139
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:56,660
be with Ye Zhao.

140
00:08:58,100 --> 00:09:00,540
I'm the princess of Ning.

141
00:09:00,780 --> 00:09:03,180
How could I abandon
my people for personal feelings?

142
00:09:03,420 --> 00:09:05,019
You think too little of me.

143
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:06,180
Your people?

144
00:09:07,780 --> 00:09:09,299
Are the Flower Slaves

145
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:11,020
not your people too?

146
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:15,420
Remove the demon root,

147
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:17,420
end the curse,

148
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:19,940
and return us to being human.

149
00:09:20,180 --> 00:09:21,060
For you

150
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:22,940
and for me,

151
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:24,660
it's a release.

152
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:29,020
If you want more time with Zhao,

153
00:09:29,060 --> 00:09:31,260
stay away from the Flower Slaves.

154
00:09:35,380 --> 00:09:36,660
I don't need your help.

155
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:39,300
I can find the demon root myself.

156
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:47,020
If you change your mind,
meet me at Ten-Mile Pavilion.

157
00:09:52,837 --> 00:09:55,407
(Martial Hall)

158
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:07,260
Just one last ingredient,

159
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:09,300
and the root-seeking worm
will be complete.

160
00:10:22,220 --> 00:10:23,500
The root-seeking worm is ready?

161
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:29,819
Just one last ingredient,

162
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:31,620
and the root-seeking worm
will be complete.

163
00:10:31,860 --> 00:10:32,940
Great!

164
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:34,699
What's the final ingredient?

165
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:36,540
I'll get it right now.

166
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:37,780
Stellar Dew.

167
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:39,540
Stellar Dew?

168
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:46,020
Zhao,

169
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:48,140
here is...

170
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:50,540
The cliff where I
removed my divine heart.

171
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:54,780
I saw how beautiful
the starry sky was here

172
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:55,979
and thought

173
00:10:55,980 --> 00:10:57,420
of bringing you to see it.

174
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:03,620
It is beautiful!

175
00:11:09,220 --> 00:11:10,260
Xi,

176
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:13,020
once we gather the Stellar Dew,

177
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,900
the root-seeking worm will be complete.

178
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:16,540
After that, we can remove the demon root

179
00:11:16,580 --> 00:11:18,180
and stay together forever.

180
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:20,219
That's wonderful!

181
00:11:20,220 --> 00:11:23,940
We'll be together forever!

182
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:38,540
Wow, it's so beautiful.

183
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:41,900
This is just breathtaking.

184
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:58,300
Mother, given the setting,

185
00:11:58,340 --> 00:11:59,219
let's have a drink.

186
00:11:59,220 --> 00:11:59,859
Alright.

187
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:00,820
Come on.

188
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,499
Cheers.

189
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:06,540
Cheers.

190
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:27,180
I, Pei Xiao, swear that I will

191
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:29,420
surpass my father and become

192
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:33,900
the most renowned
Great General of this world!

193
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:36,300
I, Baobao,

194
00:12:36,580 --> 00:12:37,540
will

195
00:12:37,700 --> 00:12:39,940
be happy every single day!

196
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:42,540
I, Chu Xihe,

197
00:12:42,740 --> 00:12:45,459
vow to bring prosperity
to the Ning State and ensure peace

198
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:47,940
and happiness for its people!

199
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:08,660
Ye Zhao's barrier has been broken!

200
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:11,380
Leave no one alive!

201
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:39,660
Proceed as planned.

202
00:13:41,220 --> 00:13:43,339
Spread the Verdant Decay
throughout the city!

203
00:13:43,340 --> 00:13:44,380
Yes!

204
00:13:48,537 --> 00:13:50,246
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

205
00:13:50,247 --> 00:13:53,096
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

206
00:13:53,097 --> 00:13:55,836
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

207
00:13:55,837 --> 00:13:57,466
♪Let the long shadows♪

208
00:13:57,467 --> 00:14:03,067
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

209
00:14:03,117 --> 00:14:04,716
♪If in a dream♪

210
00:14:04,717 --> 00:14:07,476
♪I can hear your voice♪

211
00:14:07,477 --> 00:14:10,326
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

212
00:14:10,327 --> 00:14:12,926
♪Let it be us♪

213
00:14:12,927 --> 00:14:17,716
♪drawing endlessly close♪

214
00:14:17,717 --> 00:14:19,476
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

215
00:14:19,477 --> 00:14:22,127
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

216
00:14:22,347 --> 00:14:25,066
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

217
00:14:25,067 --> 00:14:26,716
♪Not even in time♪

218
00:14:26,717 --> 00:14:32,376
♪to tell you how I feel♪

219
00:14:32,377 --> 00:14:33,916
♪If the rain won't stop♪

220
00:14:33,917 --> 00:14:36,666
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

221
00:14:36,667 --> 00:14:39,636
♪Let love go on♪

222
00:14:39,637 --> 00:14:42,186
♪Until forever♪

223
00:14:42,187 --> 00:14:46,826
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

224
00:14:46,827 --> 00:14:49,436
♪Until forever♪

225
00:14:49,437 --> 00:14:56,547
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
